data.description: Step into a world of refined comfort with this newly renovated gem in East Orange. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, and a finished basement, this property is the epitome of move-in readiness, situated in a prime location. The heart of the home is the renovated kitchen, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. A separate dining area offers an ideal space for more formal gatherings. The living room becomes a cozy haven with a wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm ambiance. Brand new carpet offers comfort, and hardwood flooring flows throughout underneath on the 1st fl. The master bedroom is a private sanctuary, complete with a convenient half bath and a spacious walkin closet. You will love the finished basement w/ its own full bathroom. Separate garage belongs to this property as well. This residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle, offering the perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless charm. Welcome to a place where where every detail has been carefully curated for a truly exceptional living experience. *New carpeting installed December 2022. Hardwood floors underneath the carpeting on first floor*
